---
// Hero component mimicking the dark mystic banner
---

<div class="relative w-full min-h-[85vh] overflow-hidden bg-slate-950 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-4 sm:px-6">
  <!-- Fondo Místico Espectacular -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://assets.cdn.filesafe.space/CabgvOcQpufVilP7BGnj/media/69bb632353d4f16c1cbb61aa.webp')] bg-cover bg-center bg-fixed opacity-50 scale-105 transform origin-center animate-[slowPan_30s_infinite_alternate]"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-950/40 via-slate-900/60 to-slate-950/95 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[#e6b866]/20 blur-[120px] rounded-full mix-blend-screen pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-[#B11252]/20 blur-[150px] rounded-full mix-blend-screen pointer-events-none"></div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-6 sm:space-y-8 p-8 sm:p-10 md:p-16 rounded-[2rem] sm:rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.37)] mx-2 sm:mx-0">
    
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-2 sm:mb-0 border border-brand-secondary/30 bg-brand-secondary/10 px-5 py-2 sm:px-6 sm:py-2.5 rounded-full backdrop-blur-md shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(230,184,102,0.15)]">
      <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 sm:w-2 sm:h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-secondary animate-pulse"></span>
      <span class="text-brand-secondary text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-sans tracking-[0.2em] sm:tracking-[0.25em] uppercase font-semibold">Sabiduría de Alma</span>
    </div>
    
    <h1 class="text-[28px] sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white font-serif tracking-tight leading-[1.2] drop-shadow-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto px-1 sm:px-0">
      Descubre Tu Mapa Numerológico con la <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-[#f4d393] via-brand-secondary to-[#c79a45] italic font-medium block mt-1 sm:inline sm:mt-0">Calculadora Cabalística Gratuita</span>
    </h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-4 pt-1 sm:pt-2">
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-3xl text-slate-200 font-sans font-medium max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed drop-shadow-md">
        Descubre el Poder de Tu Nombre y Fecha de Nacimiento con la Numerología Cabalística
      </p>
      
      <p class="text-[15px] sm:text-base md:text-xl text-slate-300/90 font-sans font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Una herramienta gratuita para revelar tu energía personal a través del lenguaje de los números
      </p>

      <div class="pt-6 sm:pt-8">
        <a href="#calculador" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#e6b866] text-slate-900 border border-[#c79a45] px-10 py-4 font-bold tracking-widest text-sm hover:bg-[#f4d393] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 rounded shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(230,184,102,0.3)]">
          PROBAR AHORA
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-down"><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="5" y2="19"/><polyline points="19 12 12 19 5 12"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  @keyframes slowPan {
    0% { transform: scale(1.05) translate(0, 0); }
    100% { transform: scale(1.1) translate(-2%, 2%); }
  }
</style>
